<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I would add <p>

/pet as you were<p>

This cancels all orders and clears the pets aggro table. This is very useful if Mez is being used for crowd control. For example, if you send in your pet against one MOB and a second hits you the pet will immediatly attack the second MOB when the first fight is over. Thus breakng Mez. This will also happen if a second MOB starts beating on your pet. This situation arises if a room spawns in the middle of a battle or if there is a delay in casting Mez.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="CENTER">
<tr>
